Slide 2 ‚Äì Problem Statement
Problem Statement

Banks process thousands of bank statements during loan and KYC verification.

Many applicants manipulate documents using tools like:

Photoshop

Canva

PDF editors

These manipulations include:

Changing balances

Editing salary amounts

Modifying transaction entries

Challenges with Manual Verification

Time-consuming

Human error

Cannot detect pixel-level or compression-based tampering

üëâ Need: An automated AI-based system to detect manipulated bank statements reliably.

Slide 3 ‚Äì Objective of the Project
Project Objective

Build an end-to-end AI system that:

Analyzes bank statements (PDF/Image)

Detects digital manipulation

Assigns a clear risk score

Generates a forensic report

Key Goals

Detect subtle tampering invisible to humans

Reduce manual verification effort

Provide explainable forensic evidence

