Our Solution

An AI-powered document forensics pipeline that:

‚úî Accepts PDF or image bank statements
‚úî Converts PDFs to images
‚úî Applies multiple image forensics techniques
‚úî Uses ML as a supporting signal
‚úî Produces a final risk score (0‚Äì100)
‚úî Generates downloadable forensic reports

üëâ Acts as a fraud detection layer for banks and fintech platforms.

