Slide 14 ‚Äì Challenges & Limitations
Challenges Faced

Calibrating forensic scores across different document types

Differentiating between:

Clean documents

Complex but genuine documents

Sensitivity of ELA and compression metrics

Synthetic data may not cover all real-world cases

Limitations

Model performance depends on quality of synthetic data

Extremely high-quality forgeries may require advanced models

OCR accuracy varies with image quality

